Name: Final Attack
Desc:
Attack skills have a chance of inflicting additional damage. Must have a Polearm equipped.
Required Skill: Pole Arm Mastery Lv. 3 or above
Lv. 20 Effect: Can learn the 4th Job Skill, 'Advanced Final Attack'
